metadata.name: 3D illustration 'Jean Michel'
metadata.description:
Among the authors who influenced his art, he distinguishes: Velasquez, El Greco, Goya, Salvador Dali, Jean-Michel Basquiat, Keith Haring, Jean Dubuffet, Robert Rauschenberg, Cy Twombly. Maxim Bashev is a contemporary avant-gardist working in multiple styles.
His works can be seen in the following exhibitions and auction houses:
Art Basel, Switzerland; Aldo Castillo, Chicago; Art in Motion - Artist for the art, USA; International Art Fair, Singapore; Art Chicago; Context Art Miami; Context Art New York; Jurmala Art fair, Latvia; Art Kiev Contemporary; Stuttgart, Germany; Singapore Gallery; Art Palm Beach-2020
